history.content: Like the title suggests. I am a senior in my last semester and I just need to pass CS 174 to graduate. I've been falling behind and need to do some catching up from now until the final. I am willing to pay for a tutor to meet maybe once or twice or maybe even thrice a week (we can discuss a schedule whenever). If anyone has taken the course and received a good grade, or knows someone who has and could use some extra money, please let me know. Thank you!
history.subject: Tutor needed for CS174
